---
---

<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-label">市民葬のらいと｜静岡県藤枝市</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      大切な方との<br />最後のお時間を<br />心を込めて
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">
      新設寺院・公営斎場と連携し、<br class="sp-br" />
      格式と温かみのあるお見送りを<br class="sp-br" />
      ご提案いたします。
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">無料で相談する</a>
      <a href="#plans" class="btn-outline">プランを見る</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-tel">
      <p class="hero-tel-label">24時間・365日対応</p>
      <a href="tel:050-8895-3811" class="hero-tel-number">050-8895-3811</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <span>SCROLL</span>
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    /* 明るいティール〜スレートブルーのグラデーション */
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2e6070 0%, #3d7a8a 45%, #4e91a3 100%);
  }

  .hero-bg::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 15% 75%, rgba(125, 156, 131, 0.25) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 20%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(46,96,112,0.15) 0%, transparent 40%, rgba(46,96,112,0.25) 100%);
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 2rem;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.6;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(46,96,112,0.3);
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1rem);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    line-height: 2;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-tel {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-tel-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .hero-tel-number {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .hero-tel-number:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-light);
  }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-scroll span {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.7), transparent);
    animation: scrollLine 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes scrollLine {
    0% { opacity: 1; transform: scaleY(0); transform-origin: top; }
    50% { opacity: 1; transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: top; }
    100% { opacity: 0; transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: top; }
  }

  .sp-br { display: none; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .sp-br { display: inline; }
  }
</style>
